languages.text: For 1 round, the Servoskull Swarm receives +10 FEL and INT. Any Signal effects continue working for 1 round after this ability was used.

traits.locale_text: For 1 round, the Servoskull Swarm receives +10 FEL and INT. Any Signal effects continue working for 1 round after this ability was used.

languages.text:
For 1 {g|Encyclopedia:Round}round{/g}, the servo-skull swarm gains +10 {g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerFellowship}Fellowship{/g} and {g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerIntelligence}Intelligence{/g}. The effects triggered by its signal {g|Encyclopedia:Ability}abilities{/g} affect targets for +1 additional round:
-<indent=5%>if the signal is replaced with another signal;</indent>
-<indent=5%>if the servo-skull swarm is destroyed;</indent>
-<indent=5%>or if the affected target moves from the servo-skull swarm further than 4 cells away.</indent>
languages.original_text:
На 1 {g|Encyclopedia:Round}раунд{/g} рой сервочерепов получает +10 к {g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerFellowship}Общительности{/g} и {g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerIntelligence}Интеллекту{/g}. Эффекты, наложенные его сигналами, продолжают воздействовать на цели в течение еще 1 раунда дополнительно, если происходит что-либо из перечисленного:
-<indent=5%>сигнал заменен на другой сигнал;</indent>
-<indent=5%>рой сервочерепов уничтожен;</indent>
-<indent=5%>цель отдалилась от него более чем на 4 клетки.</indent>

languages.text:
Der Servoschädel-Schwarm erhält 1 {g|Encyclopedia:Round}Runde{/g} lang +10 {g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerFellowship}Gefolgschaft{/g} und {g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerIntelligence}Intelligenz{/g}. Die durch seine {g|Encyclopedia:Ability}Signalfähigkeiten{/g} ausgelösten Effekte beeinflussen Ziele +1 weitere Runde:
-<indent=5%> wenn das Signal durch ein anderes Signal ersetzt wird.</indent>

-<indent=5%> wenn sich das betroffene Ziel weiter als 4 Felder vom Servoschädel-Schwarm entfernt.</indent>

languages.text:
L'essaim de servocrânes reçoit un bonus de {g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerFellowship}Sociabilité{/g} et d'{g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerIntelligence}Intelligence{/g} de +10 pendant 1 {g|Encyclopedia:Round}round{/g}. Les effets déclenchés par ses {g|Encyclopedia:Ability}capacités{/g} de signal augmentent de +1 round :
-<indent=5%>si le signal est remplacé par un autre ;</indent>
-<indent=5%>si l'essaim de servocrânes est détruit ;</indent>
-<indent=5%>ou si la cible s'éloigne à plus de 4 cases de l'essaim.</indent>

languages.text:
伺服头骨集群的{g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerFellowship}社交{/g}、{g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerIntelligence}智力{/g}提高10点，持续一{g|Encyclopedia:Round}轮{/g}。此外，若发生以下情况，它的信号{g|Encyclopedia:Ability}能力{/g}对目标造成的影响时间延长一轮：

- <indent=5%>受影响的目标朝远离伺服头骨集群的方向移动至少4格。</indent>
